description:
NOTE: I didn't realize that the computer audio wasn't uploading to the stream so that you all couldn't hear it; thus, you will have t use your imaginations in the silent spots to hear what I was hearing. 

I thought I should probably do a "year in review" type video at this point. Hope this helps to give you a sense of what I'm doing online.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/_coltonkirby
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/officialcoltonkirby/
Odysee: https://odysee.com/@ColtonKirby
